  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>K-Bot is a casual game that cleverly combines elements of classic block stacking and path planning games.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【Innovative Mechanisms that Defy Tradition】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ Actively consume parts of falling blocks to change the overall shape for elimination.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949350/extras/365de54c946ec0d22994fb3020a188af.poster.avif?t=1739446061\" width=648 height=364 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949350/extras/365de54c946ec0d22994fb3020a188af.webm?t=1739446061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949350/extras/365de54c946ec0d22994fb3020a188af.mp4?t=1739446061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ Break your body by falling blocks to form new shapes for elimination.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949350/extras/9d65222b09d5c5e110f465d769eda05c.poster.avif?t=1739446061\" width=648 height=364 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949350/extras/9d65222b09d5c5e110f465d769eda05c.webm?t=1739446061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949350/extras/9d65222b09d5c5e110f465d769eda05c.mp4?t=1739446061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ Create new shapes by eating the connecting parts of blocks and use gravity to complete elimination.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949350/extras/694b8dc5efd915227518b86f49b026d3.poster.avif?t=1739446061\" width=648 height=365 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949350/extras/694b8dc5efd915227518b86f49b026d3.webm?t=1739446061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【Addictive Game Features】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ A puzzle game that combines the thrill of Tetris with the strategy of Snake.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ Unique gameplay across multiple chapters and an endless challenge mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ Randomly generated blocks for a new layout with every challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ Special events and reward squares.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ Skin system to change your favorite appearance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ Global leaderboard: challenge the rankings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >:)</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>K-Bot is a casual game that cleverly combines elements of classic block stacking and path planning games.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【Innovative Mechanisms that Defy Tradition】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ Actively consume parts of falling blocks to change the overall shape for elimination.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949350/extras/365de54c946ec0d22994fb3020a188af.poster.avif?t=1739446061\" width=648 height=364 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949350/extras/365de54c946ec0d22994fb3020a188af.webm?t=1739446061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949350/extras/365de54c946ec0d22994fb3020a188af.mp4?t=1739446061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ Break your body by falling blocks to form new shapes for elimination.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949350/extras/9d65222b09d5c5e110f465d769eda05c.poster.avif?t=1739446061\" width=648 height=364 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949350/extras/9d65222b09d5c5e110f465d769eda05c.webm?t=1739446061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949350/extras/9d65222b09d5c5e110f465d769eda05c.mp4?t=1739446061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ Create new shapes by eating the connecting parts of blocks and use gravity to complete elimina